{
  "stem": "9963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- the soup that they cooked, in the evenings when we give out the soup, always is left over in the-- in the big tubs, to clean them out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that soup, what I cleaned out on the tubs, I took it over to the other ghetto and shared with all my friends.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That helped a lot, because I was able to take over quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And on top of that, you know, something like that goes around very fast.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And all the cooks, you know, they found out who I am, what I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was so helping them to clean and to do-- I always was so eager to work that everybody liked me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that put up more to cook.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] The leftovers would be more than average.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I had lots of leftovers to take it over and fed the people in the other ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Finally, that Ghetto A, a sickness broke out-- the typhus.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And of course, there was no hospitals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was one little hospital outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Only the prominent people could go in over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Average people, there was no room for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So people were dying like flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And sure enough, my friends got to be sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They got to be sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I said-- went to the manager, and I told him that my friends in the ghetto over there are sick, or he can help them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, well, how many you have?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, at that time, I had four friends that got sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He called up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said a taxi can enter the ghetto, and I was there, picked them up, put them in the taxi, and put them in the hospital in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was able to help.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
